		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If I had access to a real game genie, and could change it's ROM, I think I could fix it with a simple sound register reset routine, used after the start button is pressed. Short of that, you'd need at least 1 code in the game genie to fix the error, possibly more than 3.

		

